
## Making releases

 - update setup.py
 - dch -v
 - git commit
 - git tag -s numm-$VERSION -m numm-$VERSION
 - python setup.py sdist

### Updating the Debian package

Build a new source package:

 - cp dist/numm-$VERSION.tar.gz numm_$VERSION.orig.tar.gz
 - git clone . release
 - dpkg-source -b -i'(\.git|MANIFEST\.in)' release
 - rm -rf release

Build a new binary package:

 - sudo cowbuilder --update
 - sudo cowbuilder --build numm_$VERSION-$REV.dsc
 - cd /var/cache/pbuilder/result
 - dput numm_$VERSION-$REV.changes

### Updating the API documentation

 - python setup.py make_docs
 - rsync -av apidocs/ numm.org:/var/www/numm.org/numm/apidocs
 - rm -rf apidocs
